doctype html

head
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css")
body
    .start
        p You should try to #[strong #{action}] at one of the following times:
        div(style="text-align: center;")
            - for(let i = 3; i >= 0; i--)
                p.time #{time[i].hour}:#{time[i].minute} #{time[i].ampm}
        p Please keep in mind that you should be falling #[strong asleep] at these times.
        p The average human takes #[strong fourteen minutes] to fall asleep, so plan accordingly!
        p sleepyti.me works by counting backwards in #[strong sleep cycles]. Waking up in the middle of a sleep cycle leaves you feeling tired and groggy, but waking up in #[i between] cycles wakes you up feeling refreshed and alert!
